{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/rabbitmq/rabbitmq2/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"JAVA 단기 심화 부트캠프","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">RabbitMQ</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/bc51f/RabbitMQ-img.png","srcSet":"/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/41200/RabbitMQ-img.png 165w,\n/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/f979a/RabbitMQ-img.png 330w,\n/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/bc51f/RabbitMQ-img.png 660w","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/322ad/RabbitMQ-img.webp 165w,\n/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/de3b3/RabbitMQ-img.webp 330w,\n/static/56d8bd6f6c2ddafe65a35c8ba7b8954b/2b2b5/RabbitMQ-img.webp 660w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400}}}},"body":"<h2>RabbitMQ를 실습을 진행해보자</h2>\n<p>실습에 앞서 전체적인 아키텍처를 그려보면 다음과 같다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.12121212121212%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/c9b55/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 165w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/f2908/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 330w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/cc661/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 660w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/bc514/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 720w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/04c57/rabbitmq-drawio.png 165w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/d9ecf/rabbitmq-drawio.png 330w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/1f083/rabbitmq-drawio.png 660w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/37523/rabbitmq-drawio.png 720w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/1f083/rabbitmq-drawio.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"RabbitMQ 아키텍처\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>RabbitMQ 아키텍처</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Order쪽에서 market exchange를 통해 market.product, market.payment쪽으로 메세지를 전달하고 product쪽은 라운드 로빈 형식으로 로드벨런싱으로 순차적으로 받는 실습과 기본적인 메시징 큐형식으로 받아보는 payment를 실습을 진행 할거다 이번 포스팅에서는 payment쪽을 해보고 다음 포스팅때는 product쪽을 진행해보자</p>\n<h3>RabbitMQ 설치하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>도커를 사용해서 RabbitMQ를 설치 하자</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">version: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  rabbitmq:\n    image: rabbitmq:management\n    container_name: rabbitmq\n    ports:\n      - \"5672:5672\"\n      - \"15672:15672\"\n    restart: unless-stopped</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>docker-compose up 명령어로 실행하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker-compose up -d</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>localhost:15672 로 접속하게 되면 로그인페이지가 보인다. 따로 설정을 안해놨다면 아이디 비밀번호는 다음과 같다.\n<ul>\n<li>username : guest</li>\n<li>password : guset</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Order Application 생성하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>start.spring.io에 접속해서 프로젝트를 생성하자</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/c9b55/order-spring-io.webp 165w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/f2908/order-spring-io.webp 330w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/cc661/order-spring-io.webp 660w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/a66df/order-spring-io.webp 990w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/d33d4/order-spring-io.webp 1320w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/f16bf/order-spring-io.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/04c57/order-spring-io.png 165w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/d9ecf/order-spring-io.png 330w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/1f083/order-spring-io.png 660w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/7a3d6/order-spring-io.png 990w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/78958/order-spring-io.png 1320w,\n/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/bb27a/order-spring-io.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7c8f8d51f720018a69c1b141c553e425/1f083/order-spring-io.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Order Application\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Order Application</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>application.properties를 삭제하고 application.yml로 생성한뒤 다음과 같이 설정한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">spring:\n  application:\n    name: order\n  rabbitmq:\n    host: localhost\n    port: 5672\n    username: guest\n    password: guest\nmessage:\n  exchange: market\n  queue:\n    product: market.product\n    payment: market.payment</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>rabbitmq쪽은 연결하는 부분이라고 생각하면 되고</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>message쪽은 exchange와 큐의 이름을 설정하는 것이라고 생각하면 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>OrderApplicationQueueConfig.java</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import org.springframework.amqp.core.Binding;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.core.BindingBuilder;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.core.Queue;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.core.TopicExchange;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;\n\n@Configuration\npublic class OrderApplicationQueueConfig {\n\n    @Value(\"${message.exchange}\")\n    private String exchange;\n\n    @Value(\"${message.queue.product}\")\n    private String queueProduct;\n\n    @Value(\"${message.queue.payment}\")\n    private String queuePayment;\n\n    @Bean public TopicExchange exchange() { return new TopicExchange(exchange); }\n\n    @Bean public Queue queueProduct() { return new Queue(queueProduct); }\n    @Bean public Queue queuePayment() { return new Queue(queuePayment); }\n\n    @Bean public Binding bindingProduct() { return BindingBuilder.bind(queueProduct()).to(exchange()).with(queueProduct); }\n    @Bean public Binding bindingPayment() { return BindingBuilder.bind(queuePayment()).to(exchange()).with(queuePayment); }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>OrderService.java</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.core.RabbitTemplate;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n\n@Service\n@RequiredArgsConstructor\npublic class OrderService {\n\n    @Value(\"${message.queue.product}\")\n    private String productQueue;\n\n    @Value(\"${message.queue.payment}\")\n    private String paymentQueue;\n\n    private final RabbitTemplate rabbitTemplate;\n\n    public void createOrder(String orderId) {\n        rabbitTemplate.convertAndSend(productQueue, orderId);\n        rabbitTemplate.convertAndSend(paymentQueue, orderId);\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>OrderController.java</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PathVariable;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RestController;\n\n@RestController\n@RequiredArgsConstructor\npublic class OrderController {\n\n    private final OrderService orderService;\n\n    @GetMapping(\"/order/{id}\")\n    public String order(@PathVariable String id) {\n        orderService.createOrder(id);\n        return \"Order complete\";\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Order Application 실행 해보기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>실행 후 <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/order/1\">http://localhost:8080/order/1</a> 로 접속해보면 \"Order complete\"이라고 잘 뜨는걸 확인할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>localhost:15672에 접속을 해보면 다음과 같다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/c9b55/topic-made.webp 165w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/f2908/topic-made.webp 330w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/cc661/topic-made.webp 660w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/a66df/topic-made.webp 990w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/d33d4/topic-made.webp 1320w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/f16bf/topic-made.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/04c57/topic-made.png 165w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/d9ecf/topic-made.png 330w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/1f083/topic-made.png 660w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/7a3d6/topic-made.png 990w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/78958/topic-made.png 1320w,\n/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/bb27a/topic-made.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2e4cc425d63084ad48aa8e2138e5c382/1f083/topic-made.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"market exchange 생성\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>market exchange 생성</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/c9b55/queue-made.webp 165w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/f2908/queue-made.webp 330w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/cc661/queue-made.webp 660w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/a66df/queue-made.webp 990w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/d33d4/queue-made.webp 1320w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/f16bf/queue-made.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/04c57/queue-made.png 165w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/d9ecf/queue-made.png 330w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/1f083/queue-made.png 660w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/7a3d6/queue-made.png 990w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/78958/queue-made.png 1320w,\n/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/bb27a/queue-made.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0e37b057f85bb9a830a4253a8bcd413b/1f083/queue-made.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"queue 생성\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>queue 생성</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/c9b55/binding-made.webp 165w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/f2908/binding-made.webp 330w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/cc661/binding-made.webp 660w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/a66df/binding-made.webp 990w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/d33d4/binding-made.webp 1320w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/f16bf/binding-made.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/04c57/binding-made.png 165w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/d9ecf/binding-made.png 330w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/1f083/binding-made.png 660w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/7a3d6/binding-made.png 990w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/78958/binding-made.png 1320w,\n/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/bb27a/binding-made.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/df1f8093dc044fc0d1f4613087dcea0a/1f083/binding-made.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"binding 생성\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>binding 생성</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>우리가 Order Application에서 생성한 exchange, queue, binding이 생성 되어있는걸 확인 할 수가 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>아직은 프로듀서쪽에서 메세지를 전달해 큐에 적재만 되어있고 이제 payment컨슈머를 생성해서 받아보는걸 해보자</p>\n<h3>Payment Application 생성하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>start.spring.io에 접속해서 프로젝트를 생성하자</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/c9b55/payment-spring-io.webp 165w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/f2908/payment-spring-io.webp 330w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/cc661/payment-spring-io.webp 660w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/a66df/payment-spring-io.webp 990w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/d33d4/payment-spring-io.webp 1320w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/518ae/payment-spring-io.webp 1327w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/04c57/payment-spring-io.png 165w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/d9ecf/payment-spring-io.png 330w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/1f083/payment-spring-io.png 660w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/7a3d6/payment-spring-io.png 990w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/78958/payment-spring-io.png 1320w,\n/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/4cdc7/payment-spring-io.png 1327w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d983238f5f656e3e45ed49a20601ed3f/1f083/payment-spring-io.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Payment Application\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Payment Application</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>application.properties 삭제 후 application.yml 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">spring:\n  application:\n    name: payment\n  rabbitmq:\n    host: localhost\n    port: 5672\n    username: guest\n    password: guest\nmessage:\n  queue:\n    payment: market.payment</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>여기서 살펴볼 부분은 message 부분이다. Payment Application 에서 받아야 할 부분은 market.payment 이므로 Order에서 사용했던 나머지 부부은 필요하지 않다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>PaymentEndpoint.java 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import lombok.extern.slf4j.Slf4j;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.annotation.RabbitListener;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Slf4j\n@Component\npublic class PaymentEndpoint {\n\n    @Value(\"${spring.application.name}\")\n    private String appName;\n\n    @RabbitListener(queues = \"${message.queue.payment}\")\n    public void receiveMessage(String orderId) {\n        log.info(\"receive orderId:{}, appName : {}\", orderId, appName);\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@RabbitListener 어노테이션을 이용하여 queue에 적재 되어있는 메세지를 받아주고 제대로 오는지 log를 찍어 확인해보자</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.63636363636364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/c9b55/log-payment.webp 165w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/f2908/log-payment.webp 330w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/cc661/log-payment.webp 660w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/a66df/log-payment.webp 990w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/d33d4/log-payment.webp 1320w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/29105/log-payment.webp 1396w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/04c57/log-payment.png 165w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/d9ecf/log-payment.png 330w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/1f083/log-payment.png 660w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/7a3d6/log-payment.png 990w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/78958/log-payment.png 1320w,\n/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/58354/log-payment.png 1396w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/64acd634f9a5c04c31682427510a9844/1f083/log-payment.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Payment Application - log\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Payment Application - log</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>로그기록을 보면 잘오는걸 확인 할 수가 있다. 그렇다면 localhost:15672에 접속해보자</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/c9b55/payment-try.webp 165w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/f2908/payment-try.webp 330w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/cc661/payment-try.webp 660w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/a66df/payment-try.webp 990w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/d33d4/payment-try.webp 1320w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/f16bf/payment-try.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/04c57/payment-try.png 165w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/d9ecf/payment-try.png 330w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/1f083/payment-try.png 660w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/7a3d6/payment-try.png 990w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/78958/payment-try.png 1320w,\n/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/bb27a/payment-try.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/897afb7d6ec16f013a47b31bb9f970cd/1f083/payment-try.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"localhost:15672\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>localhost:15672</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>전에 적재 되어 있던 market.payment쪽에 메세지가 1에서 0으로 바뀐걸 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>다음에는..</h2>\n<p>다음 포스팅때는 product Application을 2개를 생성해서 라운드 로빈형식으로 전달 되는지 확인 해보겠다.</p>","categories":["ALL","RabbitMQ"],"date":"August 14, 2024","description":"JAVA 단기 심화 부트캠프","id":"eb1bac40-7347-5162-8c89-676f3bf8123d","keywords":["단기 심화 부트캠프","Sparta","RabbitMQ"],"slug":"/my-first-article/rabbitmq/rabbitmq2/","title":"[RabbitMQ] RabbitMQ 실습 (1)","readingTime":{"text":"5 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}